channel.title: Why does it redirect to meat spin?
channel.description:
Hey,
If you try to add moparscape to a web page and upload it why the hell does it go to meat spin.com ?
Is the web client not meant to go on the web?
If its not, why don't you guys at moparscape release one that can be used on other peoples sites?
With XML or MYSQL (If your that good) controls so the IP can be changed withpout the users knowlege..
Jamie
